law.history: Repealed 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 92, sec. 3. -- Amended 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 159, secs. 1 and 2. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 4281e-6.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Cancellation of tax stamps on cigarettes manufactured for shipment and sale outside state, or sold by resident wholesaler to nonresident retailer; refund.
